      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "TOTAL FRANKY (8) is a capable type and proved too classy last time to win by 6 lengths at this track in a handy 28.45 beating CAWBOURNE SLICK. Ran the fastest time on the program in his latest win. Form reads well for this. LOCATED (2) was big odds last time but gave a huge sight after a fast early split and ran away with a nose win at this track over 498m in 28.79. Goes well out of this box with a win and two minor placings. One of the leading chances again. CAWBOURNE SLICK (1) broke a string of placings finishing in the money two on end before a last start fourth (22.09) at this track. Form at the trip sound including seven wins. Has never missed the frame from four starts from this draw, including a win. Key runner who gets his chance to atone. BARNSLEY (6) is looking to continue his winning ways off a quick 28.78 success latest. One of the chances.",
